    <briefdescription>
<para>Type trait to add lvalue reference to a type. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Adds an lvalue reference qualifier to a type. If the type is already a reference, it returns the type unchanged.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Type</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The type to add reference to</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
@SINCE_2_5.11</para>
<para>Example usage: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structDali_1_1AddLValueReference_1a39d1fb99374eb9fa749b02969d65c183" kindref="member">AddLValueReference&lt;int&gt;::type</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>int&amp;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
